<div id="main-content">
   <div class="main-content-header">
      <p>反詐騙</p>
   </div>

   <div>
        <h3>常見詐騙犯罪型態及手法一覽表 </h3>
              <tr> 
              <td valign="top"> 
              <div align="center"> 
                <table class="MsoNormalTable" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="684" style="width: 740px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0 none; margin-left: 1.4pt"> 
                  <tbody><tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 18.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 18.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9966FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">犯罪態樣</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 18.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9966FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: 700"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">犯罪手法</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 221.7pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 218px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF"> 
                    刮刮樂、六合彩金詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 218px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">1.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">詐騙集團印製大量刮刮樂彩券寄出，收件人每刮必中鉅額獎金，當被害人打電話查詢時，對方即要求預付百分之十五稅金，然後歹徒接著又以彩金須為會員才能領取，要求再繳會費並以公司已代簽六合彩之簽注金等理由，周而復始，連環詐財。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">2.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">詐騙集團刊登或散發廣告，偽稱為某國際集團公司，業與大陸官方交涉，可獨家鎖控香港彩券局之六合彩明牌，如有失誤願理賠千萬元等為餌，向各地六合彩迷詐財。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">3.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">詐騙集團將刮刮樂置於知名商品紙箱內，使消費者誤信為廠商的酬賓活動，並以刮刮樂上之電話查詢無誤後將稅金匯入指定帳戶內。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">4.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">詐騙集團利用報紙刊登中獎名單，並在宣傳單上印有香港特區行政長官董建華的照片作為集團負責人，俾以取信民眾。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 181.8pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 207px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">信用卡詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 207px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">1.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">歹徒設法先行得知消費者信用卡內碼後，據以偽（變）造該信用卡，再勾結商家大肆消費。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">2.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">歹徒以偽造、拾得他人遺失之身分證，向銀行申請信用卡後盜刷。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">3.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">歹徒在原申請人未收到銀行寄出的信用卡前，將其攔截後盜刷。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">4.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">歹徒以空白信用卡，用打凸機、錄碼機、燙印機打上持卡人身分資料、卡號及發卡日期，複製猶如真品的信用卡，再與廠商勾結刷卡，復向銀行要求理賠後對分利益。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">5.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">被害人利用信用卡在電腦網路上購物消費，致信用卡卡號遭到網路駭客入侵攔截，繼而被冒用盜刷。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 103.6pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 81px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">行動電話簡訊詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 81px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒利用電腦傳送「中轎車」、「中大獎」之手機簡訊，使手機簡訊接收者誤以為中獎，該詐騙集團即要求民眾必先提供稅金，以保有中獎之禮品，騙取民眾之錢財或在簡訊留下一組</font></span><font size="2"><font face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">0941</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial">、</span><font face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">0951</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial">、</span><font face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">0204</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial">、</span><font face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">0209</span></font></font><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">等加值付費電話號碼，要求回電，部份用戶信以為真並以手機回電，對方即藉故聊天閒扯，延長通話時間，藉機詐取電話費用。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 101.5pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 87px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">金融卡匯款方式詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 87px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒利用一般媒體、網路或散發傳單，以超低價價格販售賣相良好之商品，待民眾電話詢價時，即稱良機不再須即刻以金融卡轉帳方式購買，再利用一般民眾不懂轉帳程序，而設計出一套繁複的操作順序指示，按照其指示操作後，轉帳成功的金額往往數十倍於原來之費用，以達到詐轉被害人存款的目的。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">網路購物詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒在網路上刊出非常低廉的商品誘使民眾匯款，再以劣品充數，交易完成後即避不見面。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 103px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">網路銀行轉帳詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 103px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒在報紙刊登廣告或散發傳單，宣稱可幫助民眾貸款、加盟、購買法拍物等，要求被害人先行至其指定銀行開戶，存入相當之權利金或保證金，並設定電話語音約定轉帳帳戶（網路銀行服務及語音查詢帳戶餘額），然後歹徒再要求被害人提供語音查詢餘額密碼及身分證件、地址等相關資料以便確認，利用電話語音轉帳功能（網路電子交易）將被害人之存款轉帳領走。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 73px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">提款機詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 73px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒利用民眾貪圖方便心理，於遊樂場所或臨時市集、夜市旁放置假提款機或在提款機鍵盤套上假鍵盤，當民眾置入信用卡或金融卡或按鍵後側錄密碼，進而盜領存款。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 79px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF"> 
                    假權狀、證照文件詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 79px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒利用精密手法，偽造、變造身分證件或政府機關核發之執照、權狀、文書等證件，實施各種詐欺行為；如偽（變）造他人身分證申領護照，或以假文件請領土地所有權狀等是。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 82px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">金光黨詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 82px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    以二人或三人一組，向被害人謊稱其中一人為傻子，身懷鉅款或金飾，利用人性貪小便宜弱點，激起被害人的貪念，以「扮豬吃老虎」方式，騙取財物，配合「調包」等手法，用假鈔或假金飾詐財。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 84px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">假元寶、金飾詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 84px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    以一人或二人一組，衣著普通，向被害人佯稱其手上有甫行挖掘出土的元寶、金條或戒指等金飾，因需款應急，願以低價出售，引起受害人貪念而購買受騙。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 102px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF"> 
                    票據詐欺（芭樂票詐欺）</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 102px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">1.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">在銀行開立支票存款帳戶，以空頭支票詐欺購得財貨，借貸或清償債務。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">2.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">以他人名義設立帳戶領取支票，或以他人名義開戶，領取支票販賣，供人開立空頭支票，以為詐欺之用。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 149px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">虛設行號詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 149px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">1.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">刊登廣告虛設行號，廣招職員，以就業為餌，詐取就業保證金。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">2.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">虛設行號出售統一發票，便利他人逃漏稅之詐欺犯罪。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">3.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">虛設公司行號，以空頭支票對外購貨或舉債，達到詐財目的。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">4.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">假稱經營事業利潤優厚，並以缺乏資金為由，利用人貪圖暴利之心理弱點，引誘入股，四處吸金詐財。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 86px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">重利型投資詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 86px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    以投資重大土地開發或專利案之暴利行業為餌，初期給予投資者些許利益甜頭，待吸金達到一定飽和點就宣布倒閉潛逃，使參加投資者遭受錢財損失。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 82px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">惡性倒閉詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 82px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    讓人誤信其公司之營業及財務狀況良好，藉以向外大舉進貨或借貸，隨後將財產化整為零，宣告倒閉，續以極低金額折成償還，並請被害人立據放棄其餘債權。此即俗稱之「破產詐欺」。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 83px; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF"> 
                    互助會詐財（倒會詐欺）</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 83px; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    以會養會並自任會頭，暗自以會員名義連續標得會款，再捲款潛逃。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">不動產售賣詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">1.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">一屋數賣：將已出售而未辦理所有權移轉登記之不動產，再次出售。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">2.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">出售人將不動產讓給買受人，趁其未辦理移轉登記之際，復將該不動產設定抵押權，向抵押權人貸款，或將已設定抵押權之不動產以無抵押之價格出售。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">3.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">以虛構事實刊登廣告誘人投資或預售房屋，以騙取定金。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 42.05pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 42.05pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">假流當品詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 42.05pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒利用人多場所擺設高級飾品或用品，並有大型招牌書明為某大當鋪流當品大拍賣，其實際價值往往為售價的十分之一以下。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">坊間調查詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    歹徒於不特定地點、會場、說明會、大型集會或路邊，以某項調查為名，並以只須填寫資料即可獲紀念品為餌，使他人填入含身份證在內之個人資料，歹徒再利用這些資料去詐領信用卡或其他有價證券等。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">保險詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">1.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">病患以行賄或其他不法方法取得不實之健康證明書，簽買人壽保險，旋即病故，由受益人領得保險金。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">2.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">將投保之房屋、汽車等產物故意破壞或謊報失竊，致使保險標的滅失，以詐領保險金。</font></span></p> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US"> 
                    <font size="2" face="Arial">3.</font></span><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">為親人、他人或自己簽買保險契約，而後謀害親人、他人或找人替死，以詐領保險金。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 19.0pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 19.0pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">詐購財物詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 19.0pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    偽稱購買，利用商人售貨牟利及商業信賴心理，於取得財貨後逃匿。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">巫術或宗教詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    利用他人迷信心理，以鬼神之說恐嚇受害人，再偽稱能為人作法、消災、去厄、解運、祈福等；或以提供命相、卜卦等勞務，遂其「騙財騙色」之目的；或以建廟、建寺等為名，向信徒募款詐財。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">重病醫藥詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    類似金光黨詐欺模式，以三至五人為一組，向罹患重病、痼疾者或其家屬，誑稱其中一人為名醫，並有珍貴名藥、偏方可醫治其病，利用被害人或其家屬之沮喪、絕望及姑且一試心理，騙取巨額醫藥費。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">假身分詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    如假冒司法調查人員收取紅包；冒用警察身分臨檢或辦案斂財；假藉公益團體騙取善款；假藉社工發放老人年金之名，騙取存摺、印章進而盜領存款；冒充星探向欲往演藝界發展少女，騙財騙色等皆是。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 40.7pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 40.7pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">勞務詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 40.7pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    假藉為人代辦事務或某特定勞務，要求預付報酬或因該工作所需之費用，詐取他人財務，如俗稱「</font></span><font size="2" face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">○○</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">黃牛」均是。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 40.7pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 40.7pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">居間詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 40.7pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    利用媒介雙方訂約機會，居間詐得他人財物。如偽稱介紹職業或介紹外籍、大陸新娘，從中騙取介紹費、保證金或代辦費等。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">打工陷阱詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    刊登廣告以高薪、工作輕鬆，徵求「公主」、「男公關」或「影、歌星」為餌，向應徵者騙取訂金、保證金、置裝費、訓練費、替代保證金等詐財。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 39.3pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 39.3pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">不法傳銷詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 39.3pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    不法業者以績效獎金及分紅制度為幌，實則以「老鼠會」傳銷商品方式，向求職者詐騙錢財與勞力。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 39.35pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 39.35pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">婚姻、交友詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 39.35pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    謊稱未婚或已離婚，利用他人急於交友、尋找婚姻對象或續絃之際，以結婚、交友為餌，詐騙對方之財物後，藉詞拖延或一走了之。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
