                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">假貨騙售詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 39.3pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    以出售不具真實價值之物品，詐取財物，如出售偽（劣）藥、偽（劣）酒牟利等。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">佯稱代辦貸款詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    於報上刊登廣告，佯稱可為急需用錢者代辦貸款事宜，藉此向被害人騙取律師（代書）代辦手續費、保證金等。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 40.0pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 40.0pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">假稱傷病、貧困詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 40.0pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    佯裝傷病、謊稱潦倒困苦，藉此博人同情，騙取車資、醫藥或生活費等。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
