                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    被害人車輛在公路（尤為高速公路）拋錨，拖吊業者於車輛拖吊或修復後，向被害人索取顯不相當之高額費用。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 39.3pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 39.3pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
