                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
                    商家出售貨品或提供服務時，將定規法碼之衡器暗動手腳，如買賣蔬果短少斤兩、計程車跑錶加速跳動等，多賺價款。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 44.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 44.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">登廣告假脫售詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 44.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2">佯稱</font></span><font size="2"><font face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">BMW</span></font><span style="font-family: Arial">、</span><font face="Arial"><span lang="EN-US">BENZ</span></font></font><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">等高級名車、名貴圖畫或貴重金飾、音響等物品急需脫售，向被害人收取訂金，並給予一張等額的支票為憑，另以需辦理過戶或其他理由騙取被害人身份證件、印鑑，即不知去向，續行詐騙。</font></span></p></td> 
                  </tr> 
                  <tr style="page-break-inside: avoid; height: 41.4pt"> 
                    <td width="152" valign="middle" style="width: 114.1pt; height: 41.4pt; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#9999FF" align="center"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">假募款詐欺</font></span></p></td> 
                    <td width="532" valign="middle" style="width: 398.9pt; height: 41.4pt; border-left-color: #EBEBEB; border-right-style: solid; border-right-color: #EBEBEB; border-top-color: #EBEBEB; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #EBEBEB; padding-left: 4px; padding-right: 4px; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px" bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
                    <p class="MsoNormal"> 
                    <span style="font-family: Arial"> 
                    <font size="2"> 
